; Minimal import definition for gdal313.dll (OSGeo4W GDAL 3.13, ECW SDK 5.5).
; Only the C-API symbols used by ecw_wrapper.c are exported here — generated
; so we can link auto_maps_ecw.dll against the prebuilt gdal313.dll without the
; OSGeo4W gdal-dev package. The actual DLL (gdal313.dll) is bundled at runtime.
LIBRARY gdal313.dll
EXPORTS
GDALAllRegister
GDALOpen
GDALClose
GDALVersionInfo
GDALGetRasterXSize
GDALGetRasterYSize
GDALGetRasterCount
GDALGetProjectionRef
GDALGetGeoTransform
CPLSetConfigOption
CPLGetLastErrorMsg
GDALWarpAppOptionsNew
GDALWarpAppOptionsFree
GDALWarp
GDALDatasetRasterIO
GDALTranslateOptionsNew
GDALTranslateOptionsFree
GDALTranslate
GDALGetDriverByName
GDALCreateCopy
GDALGetRasterBand
GDALGetRasterColorTable
